FAILURE 3+4 (both desktop + mobile): "? shortcut from / lands on /help docs landing"
  - Expected URL "http://localhost:5174/help", Received "http://localhost:5174/onboarding"
  - Root cause: the SPA at "/" redirects to /onboarding because no paired credentials
